text: Ata'eba, apani sabara karuna, yemana ucca sahasi payagambaragana sabara karechena ebam odera bisaye tarighari karabena na. Oderake ye bisaye oyada deya hata, ta yedina tara pratyaksa karabe, sedina tadera mane habe yena tara dinera eka muhurtera besi prthibite abasthana kareni. Eta suspasta abagati. Ekhana tara'i dhbansaprapta habe, yara papacari sampradaya.
